text: Louise Fiddes (born 26 March 2001) is a British Paralympic swimmer who competes in international level events. She is a world and European champion in breaststroke events. ==References== Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Welwyn Garden City Category:Paralympic swimmers of Great Britain Category:English female swimmers Category:Medalists at the World Para Swimming Championships Category:Medalists at the World Para Swimming European Championships
